librarian.feywild.initial:
Hello Stranger, welcome to the Feywild, the wonderful land of fey and magic.
Have you seen a fey yet? They are a bit shy, but with some tasty treats might help you gain their trust.
 Talk to me again if you like to know more about the Fey!
librarian.feywild.borrow: Ah! Curious about the Fey? You can borrow this book, it contains valuable information on the Fey Courts.
librarian.feywild.final: Here to return that book I borrowed you? No worries you can keep it for a while longer. Fair tidings!
librarian.feywild.found: Here to return a book you found? Ah! Curious about the Fey? If you want you can borrow it for a while. Fair tidings!
librarian.feywild.lost: You lost your book? That's ok, you can have another one!
spring_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Where Am I? Who are you? Are you tasty? Let's go on an adventure! You wanna play? I'm hungry...
quest.feywild.quest_0_message_1: Where Am I? Who are you? Are you tasty? Let's go on an adventure!
quest.feywild.quest_1_message_1: What is that? A cloud! No wait, cotton candy! It doesn't taste very sweet...
quest.feywild.quest_1_message_2: Hmm! A sheep you say? It's so fluffy!
quest.feywild.quest_1_message_3: It must be lonely thou without his friends who are all the way in the sky!
quest.feywild.quest_1_message_4: What!? It cannot fly? Flying is the best thing there is!
quest.feywild.quest_1_message_5: Wish this uhm... meep could experience the joy of flying like his friend can.
quest.feywild.quest_1_message_6: Let's make it fly! We must find away!
quest.feywild.quest_1_message_7: You're smart ...Or maybe you just have a big head.
quest.feywild.quest_1_message_8: Either way I'm sure you will find a way to make this meep fly!
quest.feywild.quest_2_message_1: You made him fly! He must have been so happy!
quest.feywild.quest_2_message_2: Wish we had taught it how to land....it's broken now...
quest.feywild.quest_3_message_1: Hey it's you!  You have to taste these red bubbles of sweetness!
quest.feywild.quest_3_message_2: Sooo good! -The little faerie tries to stuff your face with berries.-
quest.feywild.quest_3_message_3: Aaaw now they are all gone...
quest.feywild.quest_3_message_4: Maybe I shouldn't have given the last ones to you...
quest.feywild.quest_3_message_5: You owe me! Now it's your turn to make me something tasty!
quest.feywild.quest_4_message_1: What is that smell? What are you making?
quest.feywild.quest_4_message_2: A cake for me and my feykin?
quest.feywild.quest_4_message_3: No, no, no, this treasure is mine... uhm ours?
quest.feywild.quest_4_message_4: Lets quickly eat it before the other fey find out!
quest.feywild.quest_4_message_6: Phew, I'm stuffed. I think I might die. Huff puff.....got more?
quest.feywild.quest_5_message_1: Oh bravest of gullible wizards, I require your aid!
quest.feywild.quest_5_message_2: Just now I was stealing some yummy honey from the Summer Courts Yard.
quest.feywild.quest_5_message_3: I got caught by one of the Bee Knights patrolling the area and he stole my honey!
quest.feywild.quest_5_message_4: and he stole my honey! You have to steal it back for me,
quest.feywild.quest_5_message_5: and make those evil Knights pay for their crimes!
quest.feywild.quest_5_message_7: You just have to, or...we won't be friends anymore!
quest.feywild.quest_6_message_1: I hope you didn't kill one of those Summer Knights!
quest.feywild.quest_6_message_2: Jeez...I said make them pay, like make them give more honey! As payment!
quest.feywild.quest_6_message_3: Oh the Honey! Sweet! All mine now! That will teach those mean Knights.
quest.feywild.quest_7_message_2: Let's plant these saplings, so I will feel more at home!
summer_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: How dare you summon me like I am some sort of magician's pet. You better know your place....hmph
quest.feywild.quest_100_message_1: How dare you summon me like I am some sort of magician's pet.
quest.feywild.quest_101_message_2: If you seek an audience with me you will have to prove your worth to me!
quest.feywild.quest_101_message_3: Hmm...So a trial of combat! You will fight a....Golem! Yes an Iron Golem!
quest.feywild.quest_101_message_4: If you survive, I will deem you worthy to be in my presence.
quest.feywild.quest_101_message_5: If you survive....-evil giggle-...uh...cough cough...off you go!
quest.feywild.quest_102_message_1: What a battle! I had a few good laughs with your struggles,
quest.feywild.quest_102_message_2: but you pulled through in the end! Which is something.
quest.feywild.quest_102_message_3: Not much, but something. Ah so funny! Ahum...
quest.feywild.quest_103_message_1: So you have some skill with a sword...that's nice and all, but do you have wits!
quest.feywild.quest_103_message_2: To prove you worthy of being my servant and protector, you should...
quest.feywild.quest_103_message_3: get me....a bee's nest! Preferably with the bees stil inside! Yes!
quest.feywild.quest_103_message_4: We require more steeds for our cavalary...
quest.feywild.quest_103_message_5: The Queen will be pleased with my offering!
quest.feywild.quest_103_message_6: Be it the bees or this mortal's corpse....-evil giggle- uh cough cough!
quest.feywild.quest_103_message_7: Ow you still here! Now hop along and don't get stung!
quest.feywild.quest_104_message_1: That was amazing! Hope those stingers didn't hurt to much?
quest.feywild.quest_104_message_2: Or is that your normal face?
quest.feywild.quest_104_message_3: If that's the case, maybe you where better off getting stung...hehe
quest.feywild.quest_105_message_1: Maybe you are not so useless after all!
quest.feywild.quest_105_message_2: The Summer Court is constantly under attack by a group of raiders,
quest.feywild.quest_105_message_3: who hunt down our kind to grind them into dust!
quest.feywild.quest_105_message_4: We, and by we I mean you, should take down those pillagers!
quest.feywild.quest_105_message_5: Then with you as my champion we can share our victory with the Queen,
quest.feywild.quest_105_message_6: and I will be forever in her favour!! -evil giggle-
quest.feywild.quest_105_message_7: Perfect! So...why are you still standing here? Go! Now!
quest.feywild.quest_106_message_2: You did an admirable job, and I hope you will continue to slaughter any of
quest.feywild.quest_106_message_3: my enemies! My very own champion – evil giggle –
quest.feywild.quest_107_message_1: Now place these so I feel more at home ! Hmph ….-happy giggle-
quest.feywild.quest_200_message_1: Darling, what took you so long! I've been waiting for a fine specimen
quest.feywild.quest_201_message_1: Hello dear! Let's make this place a nice a comfy home.
quest.feywild.quest_201_message_2: After all we need to survive together now!
quest.feywild.quest_201_message_3: So would you be a darling and provide us with some extra food supplies?
quest.feywild.quest_201_message_4: A crate of firm potatoes, a crate of blushing red beetroots
quest.feywild.quest_201_message_5: and a crate of thick juicy carrots! That would be sooo perfect!
quest.feywild.quest_201_message_6: Let's start with getting those potatoes first!
quest.feywild.quest_202_message_1: Thank you darling! Next up I require those blushing red beetroots!
quest.feywild.quest_203_message_1: Almost done! Last on the list: thick juicy carrots!
quest.feywild.quest_204_message_1: I'm so happy you where able to get everything i asked.
quest.feywild.quest_204_message_2: I saw you sweating and working those muscles while gathering our crops.
quest.feywild.quest_204_message_3: Now that was a reward on it's own.
quest.feywild.quest_204_message_4: How about I make you a nice vegetable soup?
quest.feywild.quest_205_message_1: Hello darling, I hope you aren't too tired from all that adventuring!
quest.feywild.quest_205_message_2: I feel like our little home is lacking a bit in decorations.
quest.feywild.quest_205_message_3: Could you be so kind and procure us a few pumpkins?
quest.feywild.quest_205_message_4: I will work my magic on them!
quest.feywild.quest_206_message_1: Oh those look nice! What? The pumpkins ofcourse.
quest.feywild.quest_206_message_2: Place them anywhere nearby and if we can turn them in Jack o Lanterns
quest.feywild.quest_206_message_3: they will keep our home safe from any evil spirits who might seek
quest.feywild.quest_207_message_1: Our House is coming along so nicely!
quest.feywild.quest_207_message_2: We should provide the trees with the correct colors, don't you think?
quest.feywild.quest_207_message_3: Otherwise its going to be a boring and gray world and we see
quest.feywild.quest_207_message_4: plenty of that during the winter.
quest.feywild.quest_207_message_5: Darling, could you grab some dyes and provide us with a fabulous color pallete?
quest.feywild.quest_208_message_1: Those are some nice colors! You've got good taste!
quest.feywild.quest_208_message_2: Let's give all the happy little trees some color!
quest.feywild.quest_208_message_3: To make sure they are not alone, lets give all of them a little friend,
autumn_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Darling, what took you so long! I've been waiting for a fine specimen just like you!
winter_quest_pixie.feywild.summon_messag: Such inconvenience...why did you summon me Mortal? This ordeal will most certainly lead to your premature demise. But then maybe we can be friends...

message.feywild.music_disc_feywild_2: Song of the Seasons Composed, mixed and mastered by: Davy Habets (IKIGA)
dwarf.feywild.dialogue: <Dwarf> Beardless friend! Talking is cheap, but ores are priceless. So, let's trade!
dwarf.feywild.trade: <Dwarf> Haha, it's always great trading with you!
dwarf.feywild.scroll: <Dwarf> Haha, I like your style. Tell me if you need anything.
message.feywild.dwarf_blacksmith: Use this scroll on a Dwarven Anvil to summon your Dwarven friend.
message.feywild.autumn_pixie: A summoning scroll for a Autumn Pixie
message.feywild.spring_pixie: A summoning scroll for a Spring Pixie
message.feywild.summer_pixie: A summoning scroll for a Summer Pixie
message.feywild.winter_pixie: A summoning scroll for a Winter Pixie
message.feywild.bell.annoyed: I am here already, please be quiet!
spring_fey_thanks: Oh, for me? Thank you so much, human.
